    <string name="shopping_onboarding_add_title">Add what you need</string>
    <string name="shopping_onboarding_add_body">Tap + to pick items from your list and add them here. You can select multiple at once so the list is ready before you head out.</string>
    <string name="shopping_onboarding_log_title">Log when you buy something</string>
    <string name="shopping_onboarding_log_body">Tap ✓ next to an item and tell me how much you got. I\'ll move it to Stock right away and start tracking how long it\'ll last.</string>
    <string name="shopping_onboarding_alert_title">I\'ll tell you what\'s running low</string>
